{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Intl.DateTimeFormat.supportedLocalesOf()","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/DateTimeFormat/supportedLocalesOf","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">Standard-Objekte</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl\"><code>Intl</code></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Eigenschaften</strong></a><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/@@toStringTag\"><code>Intl[@@toStringTag]</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/getCanonicalLocales\"><code>Intl.getCanonicalLocales()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/supportedValuesOf\"><code>Intl.supportedValuesOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><strong>Ähnliche Seiten:</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/Collator\"><code>Intl.Collator</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/DateTimeFormat\"><code>Intl.DateTimeFormat</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/ListFormat\"><code>Intl.ListFormat</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/NumberFormat\"><code>Intl.NumberFormat</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/PluralRules\"><code>Intl.PluralRules</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/RelativeTimeFormat\"><code>Intl.RelativeTimeFormat</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/Segmenter\"><code>Intl.Segmenter</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong>Vererbung:</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Eigenschaften</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die <strong><code>Intl.DateTimeFormat.supportedLocalesOf()</code></strong> Methode gibt ein Array zurück, welches die Gebiete enthält, die die Datums- und Zeitformatierung unterstützen, ohne das auf das Laufzeitstandardgebeit zurückgegriffen werden muss.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/intl-datetimeformat-prototype-supportedlocalesof.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code>Intl.DateTimeFormat.supportedLocalesOf(<var>locales</var>[, <var>options</var>])</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"locales\"><code>locales</code></dt>\n <dd>Ein String mit einem BCP 47 Sprachtag, oder ein Array von solchen Strings. Für die generelle Form des <code>locales</code> Arguments siehe die <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl#gebietsidentifikation_und_-verhandlung\">Intl Seite</a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"options\"><code>options</code></dt>\n <dd>\n <p>Optional. Ein Objekt, welches die folgende Eigenschaft haben kann:</p>\n\n <dl>\n  <dt id=\"localematcher\"><code>localeMatcher</code></dt>\n  <dd>Der Auswahlalgorithmus des Gebietes. Mögliche Werte sind <code>\"lookup\"</code> und <code>\"best fit\"</code>; der Standard ist <code>\"best fit\"</code>. Für mehr Information über diese Option siehe auf der <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl#gebietsauswahl\">Intl Seite</a>.</dd>\n </dl>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rückgabewert","title":"Rückgabewert","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Gibt ein Array zurück, welches eine Untermenge der gegebenen Gebiete enthält, für die die Datums- und Zeitformatierung unterstützen wird, ohne das auf das Laufzeitstandardgebeit zurückgegriffen werden muss.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beschreibung","title":"Beschreibung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Gibt ein Array zurück, welches eine Untermenge der gegebenen Gebiete (<code>locales</code>) enthält. Die Sprachtags, die zurückgegeben werden, unterstützen Datums- und Zeitformatierungen für das entsprechende Gebiet, ohne auf den Systemstandard zurückgreifen zu müssen.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"einsatz_von_supportedlocalesof","title":"Einsatz von <code>supportedLocalesOf</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Angenommen wird, dass indonesische und deutsche Datums- und Zeitformatierung unterstützt wird, aber balinesisch nicht. <code>supportedLocalesOf</code> gibt das indonesische und deutsche Sprachtag unverändert zurück, obwohl Pinyin nicht mit Indonesisch verwendet wird und Fachdeutsch wahrscheinlich nicht für Indonesisch verfügbar ist. Zu bemerken ist, dass der <code>\"lookup\"</code> Algorithmus verwendet wird — der<code>\"best-fit\"</code> Algorithmus könnte entscheiden, dass Indonesisch eine angemessene Ergänzung für Balinesen ist, da die meisten Balinesen Indonesisch verstehen und daher auch das balinesische Sprachtag zurückgeben.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> locales <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'ban'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'id-u-co-pinyin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'de-ID'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> options <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">localeMatcher</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'lookup'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Intl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>DateTimeFormat<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">supportedLocalesOf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>locales<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> options<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">join</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">', '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// → \"id-u-co-pinyin, de-ID\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Einsatz von supportedLocalesOf"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-402/1.0/#sec-12.2.2\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript Internationalization API 1.0 (ECMA-402)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Intl.DateTimeFormat.supportedLocalesOf' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initiale Definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-402/2.0/#sec-12.2.2\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript Internationalization API 2.0 (ECMA-402)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Intl.DateTimeFormat.supportedLocalesOf' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma402/#sec-Intl.DateTimeFormat.supportedLocalesOf\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript Internationalization API (ECMA-402)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Intl.DateTimeFormat.supportedLocalesOf' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Intl.DateTimeFormat.supportedLocalesOf","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/DateTimeFormat/supportedLocalesOf/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/DateTimeFormat\"><code>Intl.DateTimeFormat</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beschreibung","id":"beschreibung"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die Intl.DateTimeFormat.supportedLocalesOf() Methode gibt ein Array zurück, welches die Gebiete enthält, die die Datums- und Zeitformatierung unterstützen, ohne das auf das Laufzeitstandardgebeit zurückgegriffen werden muss.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Intl.DateTimeFormat.supportedLocalesOf()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Intl.DateTimeFormat.supportedLocalesOf()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Intl.DateTimeFormat.supportedLocalesOf()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Intl.DateTimeFormat.supportedLocalesOf()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/intl/datetimeformat/supportedlocalesof","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/intl/datetimeformat/supportedlocalesof/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"JavaScript-Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Globale Objekte"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl","title":"Intl"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/DateTimeFormat","title":"Intl.DateTimeFormat"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/DateTimeFormat/supportedLocalesOf","title":"Intl.DateTimeFormat.supportedLocalesOf()"}],"pageTitle":"Intl.DateTimeFormat.supportedLocalesOf() - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}